A:   Because he was an asshole.

Q:   And describe how he behaved.

A:   He was saying things to me like---I don't know--"You two should be
apart. She should leave you." and I said something to him, "I thought you
were supposed to be diffusing this situation here," and he made another
comment, and I said, "Well, who are you to be saying this to me " And at that
