Q:  Over Nicole?

A:   Yeah, I think over--I can't recall. It  just seemed that sometimes there was
a couple of  conflicts time-wise, where Paula wanted to do  something but I
had told the kids I'd do something,  and then Nicole would end up with me
and the kids  doing something.

Q:   It's fair to say that the conflicts that you had with Paula during this time
