mother, and I believe on one of of those occasions she was there or was
coming the next day, and I called the next day to talk to her, but if it was three
or four times in that year, it would have been the most. Paula called, I know,
the day Marcus was getting married. You know--

Q:   She write to you?

A:   No.

Q:   And you to her?

A:   No.

