never left her at that point in our relationship, and I was--you know, I  had to
try to understand how I felt, and the kids  obviously was in the mix, but I
think it was about  myself first.

Q:  Now, over the next year you saw Nicole on a monogamous basis. Right?

A:   Yes.

Q:  And then split up with her the day after  Mother's Day of 1994. Is that
