Q:  For what purpose?

A:   That was what I and her always--No, I  didn't. I didn't. That would have
been the next  month I was gonna do that, so I don't think I did.

Q:  What was the purpose that you--

A:   Unless Sydney was graduating or something, yeah.

Q:  What was the purpose for which you would exchange flowers that time of
