A:  Yeah. I don't sometime. I always take at least one walk around my
house at night.

Q:  Because of insomnia? You can't sleep?

A:  No. I check on my kids, look out at the dogs, you know, take a
leak. It's just always been my practice.

Q:  Does the dog normally sleep outside?

A:  Yes.

Q:  Chachi?

A:  Yes.

