A:  Just opening a door and getting in the car normally, and you kinda use
your hands, the steering wheel and the door thing.

Q:  Do you recall getting inside the car?

A:  Yeah, I leaned in. I had to lean in and ended up getting it, and I ended up
getting a jacket.

Q:  Did you physically get inside the car?

A:  I'm sure my body had to be inside the car to an extent, yes.

Q:  Okay. Well, did you get into the car and sit in the driver's seat?

A:  I don't believe so.

Q:  Okay. When you're talking about getting in the car, you are talking about
