A:  Well, as I told you, I was putting a few things together, a few nights
were running together, Saturday night, Sunday night was running together,
and if you look at my cell phone records, you will see at roughly this time on
Saturday, as I was going to Paula's house, I called her.

Q:  Okay.

A:  So there were -- I hadn't slept, and last night was whatever night it was
to me, and the nights were running together to me at this time.

