A:  I grabbed something, yes.

Q:  And what did you grab?

A:  Toilet paper.

Q:  Okay. Did you also grab a washcloth?

A:  Maybe .

Q:  Maybe meaning you don't recall?

A:  Correct.

Q:  Okay. So you have no recollection as to whether you used a washcloth in
