THE WITNESS: I knew sometime that morning. I knew--by the 
time I got back to L.A., I knew A.C. had. I'm not sure if I thought 
both A.C. and Arnelle had, but I knew A.C. was involved. I knew 
A.C. was driving. 
 
BY MR. KELLY: 
Q: Okay. And you knew that when you were still on the flight 
