A: Yeah, it's like you'd work with a person, yes. 
 
Q: Okay. And you would often learn these right on location when 
you were getting ready for these movies? 
 
A:  No.  I'd study my script and know my part and then work out 
the movements on the set. 
 
Q:  Okay.  Since June 12th, 1994 have you ever--have you given 
