week?  
 
A: Yes. 
 
Q: Okay.  What days were they?   
 
A: Every day.  
 
Q: And it's your usual practice, I assume, to wear a golf glove.  
 
A: Yes.  
 
Q: Except for par 3s?  
 
A: Yes.  
 
Q: That was always on your left hand, was it not?  
 
A: Yes. MR. KELLY: Take a break?  
 
MR. ROBERT BAKER: Sure.  
 
