something for  whatever reason, you're very cautious about that. 
Just the way I've always been.  
 
Q: In any particular sport or just any sport when you have a 
headache?  
 
A:  Any sport. I mean, even my kids. If my kids had an accident, 
and, you know, we wouldn't let them sleep. We try to keep them 
awake.  If they said their head hurt in any way, shape or form, 
that's just something that you do.  
 
Q: So you're talking about a concussion-type situation, are you 
not?  
 
A: Yes. 
 
Q:  Okay. So we are talking about contact incidences, are we not?  
 
A: Yes. 
 
Q:  Okay. And it was your concern about contact and concussions 
