didn't really buy me that bracelet, did you?" Because even the day I 
gave it to 
 
her she was surprised.  
 
Q: Was it a tennis bracelet?  
 
A: No.  
 
Q: Could you describe it to me?  
 
A: I think it was sapphires and diamonds. It was kind of an antique, 
