bought it for her, and she couldn't understand why I had bought it 
for her, and I told her, "The kids bought it for you." 
 
And she says, "You didn't really buy me this," and I didn't say 
anything, and so she gave it back to me, and I was sorta glad to get 
it back.  
 
Q: Who did you buy that bracelet for?  
 
A: Paula.  
 
Q: When did you buy it?  
 
A: I think on the 19th. 
 
Q:  When you spoke to the police on the 13th, who did you tell 
