Sydney and Justin?

A: Yeah, we talked about-well, Sydney was there; we were watching her,
and just-we just basically talked generally about our children, mine
and his.

Q: Did he say anything to you about the effect on the children of his
splitting up with Nicole?

A: No. He always, and I don't know if it was at this time or not, but
he always said what a good mother Nicole was and how, you know, he
could leave town and go on a business trip and not have to worry about
the kids and how it was great that she was such a good mother. Beyond
that, I don't really recall, you know, anything in depth about the
children.

Q: Prior to Nicole's death did you know about an affair between or
relationship between Marcus Allen and Nicole?

A: No. Never heard about it until the trial.

