A: No, I did not.

Q: Or to the policeman or detectives around him?

A: No. They were on the property, and I wasn't allowed on the
property.

Q: Did you try to get the bag into  Mr. Weitzman's car?

A: No. No, I did not.

Q: Or the detectives' car?

A: No.

