Q: What was your purpose in going over there that morning?

A: Just to console him, just to be, you  know, a good friend basically
and sit with someone.

Q: Okay. And when you got there, you took the bag upstairs. Right?

A: Yes, sir.

Q: Right up to the bedroom?

A: Yes.

Q: And why was that?

A: Because that's where he was, so I knew that's where his closet was,
