A: Either in the black grip or in-I know the black grip was open. It
was on the floor, and I know he put a few things in there. Whether he
put some things in the Louis Vuitton bag, I don't know.

Q: Did you talk about how many days he would, spend at your house?

A: Yes.

Q: What did he say?

A: He didn't say too much. I-I was the one who suggested, "Why don't
you come and spend a couple days at my home, and then you could come
back here in a couple of days, and this will all blow over and you can
come back."

Q: Did he say anything to you about his children at that time?

A: He could have. Could have at that time.

Q: What did he say?

A: He could have said-I'd be guessing, so I don't know. I mean, I knew
they were in Laguna because he told me they were down in Laguna and he
said he wanted to see his children, but beyond that I don't recall.

Q: And the bag was then taken with his -- the Vuitton bag and the
