A: No. The Vuitton bag was taken to my car. He kept the black bag.

Q: But you both got in your car. Right?

A: No. This is when he went out the back way, and I put the Louis
Vuitton bag in my car.

Q: Picked him up -

A: Picked him up on the corner, and he had the black bag on his
