lawyer?



MR. LEONARD: I am going to object to anything  that occurred between,

you know, he and I as attorney-client privilege.



But go ahead.



THE WITNESS: I've seen this. I've kinda  flipped through it before --



BY MR. PETROCELLI:



Q: I know. That's what you said. You said you didn't read it

