A: I wondered who -- who and -- who he was, finding out what happened.

I found out that Nicole  had died, and I found out that somebody else

at that  time had died, too.



Q: And how did you find out who he was?



A: I think the news.



Q: Did you speak to any person about who  Ron Goldman was?



A: Probably, but I don't remember specifically.



Q: Tell me who you spoke to.



A: In the last two years, everybody I've ever spoken to?



Q: No. About Ron Goldman to find out who he  was.



A: I never -- I heard from the news, from the media, from TV, who he

was.



Q: Other than the news and the media, conversations that you have had

with people.



A: Never.



Q: No one.



A: No one.



Q: Did Nicole ever discuss with you before her death that she was

dating someone or seeing someone who was a waiter at a restaurant?



A: No, sir.



