MR. LEONARD: Objection. Same basis.



THE WITNESS: Just a feeling.



BY MR. PETROCELLI:



Q: Just a feeling you have?



A: Feeling in my heart, feeling in my head.



Q: It's not something that you would want to believe to be true.



A: Of course not.



