A: Early '80s maybe. I'm sorry -- yeah, early '80s, late '70s.



Q: Late '70s? You were a young boy?



A: Yeah, ten, nine, maybe earlier. Seven. I mean, I know he was seeing

Nicole while my mom was married.



Q: How do you know that?



