A: First time I really -- first time I met  her I didn't know it was

her. First time I officially  met her had to be '81.



Q: The first time --



A: I don't know. It's a long time ago.



Q: The first time you met her when you didn't know it was her was

when?



A: My dad took me and a friend to see THE CHAMP, and Nicole and Denise

were there, and my dad said, "Look at those two girls. You think

they're pretty?" I mean, he knew them already.



Q: I see. But he didn't tell you.



A: He didn't think it right that I met them  yet, so it was just too

soon.



