MR. LEONARD: Objection. Lack of foundation,  calls for speculation.



THE WITNESS: Am I aware of it?



BY MR. PETROCELLI:



Q: Yes. Do you have any information to that effect?



A: No.



MR. LEONARD: Same objection.



BY MR. PETROCELLI:



Q: Excuse me?



A: No.



Q: No? Okay.  Do you know whether or not your father ever took a lie

