A: No, I didn't.



Q: What did you do on the morning of the 14th, Tuesday morning?



A: I got no clue. I have no idea. I was in a haze, a haze that whole

week. I don't remember. Probably cried all morning, sat on the bed.



Q: Have you ever talked to any members of he Brown family as to the

