A: No.



Q: At no time?



A: No. He had told me that he went to McDonald's, but that was it.

That's all he said.



Q: Okay. Do you play golf?



A: No. It's too boring.



Q: Do you have golf clubs?



A: No, sir.



Q: Were you familiar with your father's luggage as of June of 1994?



A: No, I wasn't.



Q: Would you have recognized his golf bag or his travel -- his golf

