A: I gotta tell you, the whole garage is lined up with golf bags. I

don't know which one is his -- his favorite or something. I'm telling

you, he's got like 20, 30 golf bags in his garage, so I really

couldn't -- I couldn't even answer that.



Q: Prior to Nicole's murder, did you ever see your dad hit golf balls

