A: Close advisors? Yeah, a couple. I mean...



Q: Who is that?



A: I call my mom someone I talk to and console, talk to a lot.



Q: Do you have a godparent?



A: A.C.



Q: He's your godparent --



A: He's my godfather, yeah.



Q: Did you attack the restaurant owner with a knife?



MR. LEONARD: Objection.



THE WITNESS: No.



