THE WITNESS: Go ahead. I don't care. Paul will tell you I didn't.



MR. PETROCELLI: Goes to --



MR. LEONARD: Oh, yeah, sure. Don't even say it.



THE WITNESS: Paul would tell you there was no damn knife involved.



